data.description: This home, BUILT 2018, is located in the desirable city of Poinciana. An OVERSIZED DRIVEWAY awaits along a THREE-CAR GARAGE, LOW HOA (with CABLE and INTERNET INCLUDED) and NO CDD. As one makes their way toward the front door, GARDEN TERRAZZO-like balls decor the greenery and complement the EXTERIOR 4-BOARD CLOSED BOARD and BATTEN SHUTTERS. Walking in the home, an ALL-CONNECTING downstairs area welcomes you to enjoy the room of preference within seconds. Here, we have an INFORMAL FAMILY ROOM to the right, and a WOOD-ACCENTED WALL to the left, that works as a MUD AREA. Following the mud area is a hallway that gives access to the THREE-CAR GARAGE, the DOWNSTAIRS guest BATHROOM, the ALARM PANEL and a FLEX ROOM with an ample STORAGE CLOSET. Adjacent to this room is the large family room that connects to the DREAM KITCHEN. Here, one can enjoy the luxury of GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, 40-INCH CABINETRY, BACKSPLASH decor with a triad-color gradient-like effect, 30-INCH GE BUILT-IN TOUCH CONTROL INDUCTION COOKTOP, 30-INCH STAINLESS STEEL WIDE DUAL WALL OVEN, GE STAINLESS STEEL FRIDGE and GE STAINLESS STEEL DISHWASHER. The ISLAND also features GRANITE COUNTERTOPS and has its own SINK WITH PULL-OUT FACUET and DUAL SPRAY MODE. Heading up the stairs, another SPACIOUS area welcomes you, the upstairs flex area, perfect for a "work-from-home" set-up, game-playing or movie-watching, lounging, or any other activity of preference. Close by, one may find the master bedroom that is glorified with a nice walkway, a beautiful TRAY CEILING, and plenty of NATURAL LIGHT. As expected, the WALK-IN closet does not let down, as it is also very spacious, side-by-side to master bathroom that features a WALK-IN SHOWER. Back in the upstairs flex-room, one has access to head to the other 3 sizable bedrooms, the second full bathroom (with its TUB), and the conveniently located LAUNDRY ROOM, WITH NO NEED TO HEAD DOWNSTAIRS. This home boasts a desirable COVERED-SCREENED-IN-LANAI (in the back, first level), adorned with hanging Thomas-Edison-like bulbs, for a time that suits your lifestyle, whether a peaceful afternoon or a night of entertainment. Lastly, the outside also counts on an IN-WALL PEST CONTROL SYSTEM for easy treatments and your convenience. This is the home you've been searching for!    *All measurements are estimates. Please confirm any restrictions with HOA.*
